    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices used for producing bobbins that are evenly covered with yarn, used to wind thread or yarn around a bobbin. These usually include a fixed shaft that is rotated continously, distributing the thread uniformly onto the mounted bobbin.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
